---
title: Moroccan-Inspired Chicken Thighs with Zucchini, Zesty Rice and Lemony Yogurt
description: This one's in the running to be your next weeknight fave! Warm, fragrant spices and creamy yogurt are a perfect quick marinade for chicken thighs, while zesty rice rounds out the flavours on this delicious Moroccan-inspired plate.
